reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 14, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This little outfit is sooooo cute!!! I bought the black set. The shorts are not too short, the crop top is not too short. It’s very comfortable. The material feels nice. It’s not see through. I am 5’9, 160lbs. I have longer legs, thicker thighs and a bigger booty. I am a 34D on top. I am self conscious of my armpit fat, I call them my chicken nuggets. 🙃 This square top completely hides my chicken nuggets! I am 44, I don’t usually buy anything with a crop top, when I saw this on an influencer, I liked the look of the crop top without the exposure of the mid section. I bought the large, I can be a medium or a large. When in doubt, online ordering, I usually opt for Large just incase. I also read the reviews about it shrinking. How it looked on her is exactly how it looked on me. I am not sure if the medium would have been too small. The shorts seemed to be higher waisted on some of the pics in the reviews but that could also be body type. It does not make me love this outfit any less. It’s adorable!! It didn’t have any weird smells. Yes, it’s slightly wrinkled but it’s a linen look, that’s what it does. I think any age can wear this outfit. When I tried it on, I sent a pic to my 19 year old daughter and she loved it too and wants to borrow it, we’re the same size and build. I can’t say enough, buy this outfit, you won’t regret it. I am about to buy another color!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So cute but runs small, size up
reviews.reviewText: This set is so cute, it’s exactly what I was looking for. I followed the recommendations of other reviewers and sized up. I’m normally a size 2/4 or a small, I bought a medium and it fits really well. The waistband is where it runs small, so the top is slightly larger than I would normally wear but it still looks really nice. The quality is very nice for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: For reference I am 5'4", 155 lbs. I purchased this outfit in light brown. Typically I wear a Medium or an 8/10 in dresses and outfits like these. Returned the original order because the shorts have an invisible zipper on the side and it was broken. I did however find the top and bottom to be a little too small and returned it for a Large so I can hand-wash in cold water and line dry. I would NOT recommend putting this outfit in the dryer as some have asked. For sure, linen shrinks and there is linen in the fabric. The color is more of a terra cotta, but really pretty. Fabric has movement and it looks expensive. Shorts hit at the perfect length and the top hit exactly where I had hoped - without showing any belly. Great little outfit for the price. I liked it so much I also ordered it in Large in Black.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 2, 2023
reviews.reviewText: 1st try on was adorable. Comfortable and cute. One wash later, the top shrunk significantly. Shorts held up slightly better than top. Not sure what happened 😕 Can't wear anymore. What a waste of $$. Disappointed

reviews.reviewText: Size up if you’re heavy chested. Good quality material and well made two piece! Light weight. I ordered light tan. The color is more orange than tan but still a nice color. Very happy with the outfit.

reviews.reviewTitle: Not linen, not the advertised colour, and way too small
reviews.reviewText: As soon as I opened the bag I was disappointed. The material feels cheap, and doesn't even try to hide the fact that it is mostly polyester. Not a trace of linen. Instead of a beige colour, the set came coloured pale yellow. I used the sizing guide and ordered a large, but the outfit fits more like a small or extra small. I will be returning this since it does not remotely resemble what I thought I was buying.
